pos_mean_info_list.mean: 消防队员；救火队员；锅炉工

bilingual.source: Firefighter, member of a fire department who fights fires.
bilingual.target: 消防队员消防队中灭火的成员。

bilingual.source: He’s a firefighter, so he has to exercise often.
bilingual.target: 他是个消防队员，所以他必须经常锻炼。

bilingual.source: Andrea Clark is a 15-year veteran firefighter and paramedic.
bilingual.target: 安德烈亚·克拉克是一名有着15年资历的消防队员和医疗急救队员。

bilingual.source: I work as a firefighter and my wife is a nurse.
bilingual.target: 我的工作是消防队员，而我太太是护士。

bilingual.source: The firefighter made a valiant effort to save the child from the burning house.
bilingual.target: 消防队员奋勇地从着火的房子里救出孩子。

bilingual.source: Identify chigger bites with tips from a firefighter in this free first aid video.
bilingual.target: 消防队员从恙螨叮咬识别技巧在这个自由急救视频。

bilingual.source: Is it still correct if it is translated into "Maybe he's going to quit as firefighter. "?
bilingual.target: 句子的意思是：可能他将不再从事消防队员这个工作。

bilingual.source: A federal task group developed a wildland firefighter fitness program to improve health and safety.
bilingual.target: 联邦工作组制定了一个荒地消防队员健身计划以改善健康和安全。

bilingual.source: That photo of the firefighter and the koala provides at least one bright spot in a very dark situation.
bilingual.target: 该照片的消防队员和考拉提供至少一个亮点，在一个非常暗的情况。

bilingual.source: A firefighter works to extinguish forest fires on the outskirts of the Russian city of Voronezh, July 30, 2010.
bilingual.target: 一个消防队员在灭火工程的沃罗涅日，2010年7月30日俄罗斯城市郊区的森林火灾。

yingyinNormal.en: Oh. Good. Yeah, do you mind me asking what he does for a living? He's a firefighter. Oh. Interesting.
yingyinNormal.zh: 很好。你介意我问一下他是干哪一行的吗？他是消防员。有意思。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, sir? Can I ride out there with you guys? Sure. What are you doing? Shane. Shane, you're not a firefighter.
yingyinNormal.zh: 先生，我能跟你们一起去吗？当然。你要干什么，Shane？Shane，你又不是消防员。

yingyinNormal.en: Because I have an audition next week. I'm playing a serious firefighter. So you're an actress. I thought you look familiar. Have I seen you on anything?
yingyinNormal.zh: 因为我下周有个试镜。我将出演一个严肃的消防员。所以你是个演员。你看起来很眼熟，我在哪个节目上见过你吗？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a person whose job is to stop fires from burning

examination_example.sentence: As well as damage from the heat,experts also need to assess damage from the vast quantities of water <highlight>firefighters</highlight> poured into the cathedral.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 除了高温造成的损失之外，专家还需要评估消防员向大教堂注入的大量水造成的损失。

examination_example.sentence: He praised the actions of the <highlight>firefighters</highlight> but admitted the fate of the cathedral had been uncertain.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 他赞扬了消防队员的行动，但承认大教堂的命运并不确定。

examination_example.sentence: The timely action of the <highlight>firefighters</highlight> prevented the fire from reaching the Cathedral's bell towers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 消防队员的及时行动阻止了大火蔓延到大教堂的钟楼。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全四级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2016-2023年8年间试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a person whose job is to stop fires from burning

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Firefighters</highlight> responded to a fire Wednesday night at an abandoned mall in Heyward.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 周三晚上，消防队员在海沃德一个废弃的购物中心应对火灾。

examination_example.sentence: <highlight>Firefighters</highlight> will remain on the scene until later this morning to ensure that the fire doesn't start up again.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 消防人员将在现场待到今天上午晚些时候，以确保火灾不会再次发生。

examination_example.sentence: It had burned for 45 minutes by the time <highlight>firefighters</highlight> arrived.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 消防队员赶到时，大火已经燃烧了45分钟。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2018-2021年全国重点省市中考试卷，包括听力、阅读、完形、单选、填空、改错、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选各省市考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2018-2021年4年间全国各省市中考试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

sense_info_list.en: a person whose job is to stop fires from burning

examination_example.sentence: Firefighters arrived and after searching the closet and narrow beds in another bedroom.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 消防员赶到现场，搜查了另一间卧室的壁橱和狭窄的床。
